metadata.name: Placeholdooor
metadata.description:
Creators have until January 2nd @ 12PM ET to deploy contracts and mint at least 1 token to maintain collection (contract) eligibility for OpenSea royalties without blocking zero-royalty marketplaces.

Future-proof your work by deploying contracts and minting your contract's first token NOW. Prepping for a future collection? Deploy a new contract and mint a single token with placeholder artwork and metadata to use later!
